text: evac_demo7 is an Indian cricketer who plays for Maharashtra. He made his List-A debut for Maharashtra against Goa in the 2018-19 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 19 September 2018. He made his first-class debut on 27 January 2020, for Maharashtra in the 2019–20 Ranji Trophy. ==References== == External links== * Atharva Kale at ESPN Cricinfo Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Maharashtra cricketers
